u <- expression(x^0.33+y^0.33-z^0.33)
# 
uxyz<-deriv(u,c("x","y","z"),func=TRUE)
x<-seq(from=0,to=20,by=0.01)
y<-seq(from=0,to=20,by=0.01)
z<-seq(from=0,to=20,by=0.01)
res<-uxyz(x,y,z)
plot(res)
